Written evidence submitted by Professor Michael Sheehan (ESA012)[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]How resilient is the UK’s space-based infrastructure? Are threats from space debris or solar activity being appropriately mitigated? What role do, or should, ESA and the UK Space Agency play in addressing these issues?
